Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:23:00.62,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}全部如愿之后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:05.72,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们还会贪婪地没有休止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:10.00,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}直到开始后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:12.65,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}永远过不够的昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:15.04,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}和不断积蓄的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:20.76,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就这样重叠着伴我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:26.97,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够成为非常喜欢的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:32.04,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}非常喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:37.20,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}连这样的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:41.94,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我还无法完全相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:46.64,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}总是难以如愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:52.36,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想再长高一些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:54.74,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愿我可以笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:57.22,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}用幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:24:00.46,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}为明天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:05.20,EDC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}命名
